{"tid":1911013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"面對任何分化狗post，都要記住村上春樹教我哋嘅原則做人","createTime":"2020-03-05T05:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T08:38:30.000Z","uid":24730,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"10450872179e22f80428a0e0a32f1bf3d788729c","tid":1911013,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T05:11:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">喺雞蛋與高牆之間，無論雞蛋點錯都好，無論高牆點啱都好，我都會企喺雞蛋嘅一邊。<br />\n<br />\n露宿者係會吸毒，但相比濫權濫捕嘅高牆，佢哋都只係雞蛋，唔好畀班黑狗分化到。<br />\n<br />\n本土派、泛民、勇武、和理非...無論邊個點錯都好，佢哋喺支共、港共、建制派面前，亦都只係雞蛋，我永遠只會幫雞蛋，絕對唔會幫高牆。</span></span>"},{"pid":"5ff77444399dc4252fa3380800cda87cad860179","tid":1911013,"uid":201464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T05:14:27.000Z","msg":"不過熱城派視泛民為高牆"},{"pid":"61fc2ba5ab1f76fe001fd587897b3c710398e875","tid":1911013,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T05:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i